 spectroscopy may be a source of\ncomplementary information. At last, we discuss how the Boltzmann energy\ndistribution, among molecular or atomic levels, may become sensitive to\nspecific thermal exchanges at the surface, in an equilibrium situation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Oct 2018 07:47:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-31"}
