d by weak and frequent nanoflares (delay less\nthan 500 seconds) or by very short and intense nanoflares that lead to\nnon-equilibrium ionization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Oct 2018 11:10:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-12"}
